      "type": "explanation",
      "content": [
        { "type": "title", "value": "Essential Particles" },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Cantonese is famous for its sentence-final particles. These small words don't have a meaning on their own but change the 'flavor' or mood of a sentence. Let's look at three essential ones: <strong>呀</strong> (aa3), <strong>喇</strong> (laa3), and <strong>嘅</strong> (ge3)."
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "好呀",
          "romanization": "hou2 aa3",
          "translation": "Okay / Good (Softened with 'aa3')"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "<strong>喇</strong> (laa3) often indicates a change of state, like 'already' or 'now'. <strong>嘅</strong> (ge3) is used for possession (like 's in English) or to emphasize a characteristic."
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "我去食飯喇",
          "romanization": "ngo5 heoi3 sik6 faan6 laa3",
          "translation": "I'm going to eat now / already"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "cantonese": "我嘅",
          "romanization": "ngo5 ge3",
          "translation": "Mine (My + 'ge3')"
        }
      ]
    },
    { "type": "reading", "exerciseId": "3.5.2" },
    { "type": "unscramble", "exerciseId": "3.5.3" },
    {
      "type": "dialog",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "我去食飯喇。",
          "romanization": "ngo5 heoi3 sik6 faan6 laa3.",
          "translation": "I'm going to eat now."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "cantonese": "好呀。呢個係咩嘢嘅？",
          "romanization": "hou2 aa3. ni1 go3 hai6 me1 je5 ge3?",
          "translation": "Okay. What is this?"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "A",
          "cantonese": "係我嘅。",
          "romanization": "hai6 ngo5 ge3.",
          "translation": "It is mine."
        },
        {
          "speaker": "B",
          "cantonese": "係唔係呀？",
          "romanization": "hai6 m4 hai6 aa3?",
          "translation": "Really?"
        }
      ]
    },
